<emphasis bold="true" box="[180,880,1040,1074]" pageId="54" pageNumber="654">Movements, Home range and Social organization.</emphasis>
No information.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="54" pageNumber="654" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="54.[178,1385,739,1231]" pageId="54" pageNumber="654">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[180,532,1083,1112]" pageId="54" pageNumber="654">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Not assessed on The IUCN Red List. Suntsov’s Marmoset Rat seems to have a restricted distribution, but the only known population is in Bu Gia Map National Park.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
